{"tid":1827738,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"澳門今年旅客料跌10%　業界去年現裁員情況","createTime":"2020-01-17T07:35:37.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-17T15:06:40.000Z","uid":60281,"like":33,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":53,"replies":[{"pid":"bfe8455ebd3155041a18adff9278c6c347e9b76f","tid":1827738,"uid":60281,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-17T07:35:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n香港反修例風波牽連比鄰的澳門。<span style=\"color: red;\">澳門旅遊業議會預料，若香港局勢持續，澳門今年整體旅客數字跌幅將遠高於旅遊局預計的3%</span>，估計跌幅可能會擴大至10%；又預料農曆新年期間，澳門旅客來源依然以自由行居多，並按年將有輕微下調。會方對澳門旅遊業前景持謹慎樂觀態度，並希望重現港澳聯遊的勢頭。<br />\n<br />\n旅遊業議會稱，內地旅客仍以港澳聯遊為主，旅遊業界推出的純澳門遊及大灣區聯遊，只是補充旅客不足，並指有部分業界自去年下半年起情況轉差，出現減薪或裁員的情況。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20200117/mobile/bkn-20200117141327345-0117_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20200117%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20200117141327345-0117_00822_001.html&d=yrakYkBpMe8E3VCHF0kcyviPq%2FHqG0pMUyXzarzxqBM%3D&h=e1420336\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20200117/mobile/bkn-20200117141327345-0117_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"3e1fa6d036f126a37c00f3655b1c1aeccef9f2ae","tid":1827738,"uid":13170,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-17T07:36:49.000Z","msg":"不如賴埋地硬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"12b48d50776c7b24ee322b4644b863b87951b05e","tid":1827738,"uid":155431,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-17T07:37:34.000Z","msg":"屌😂"},{"pid":"5e484cab6ac359b93d84fe3ffda1277120dd2680","tid":1827738,"uid":318980,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-17T07:37:42.000Z","msg":"因為香港人都唔比入境"},{"pid":"fc46a92f8cf63347c84f9a636155dce8467413e9","tid":1827738,"uid":2054,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-17T07:37:54.000Z","msg":"痴撚線咁都有得賴<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class